{"uuid":"0c06a71f-15a0-4ddd-bb00-bd1bb39ab925","type":"360e8515-6962-4365-8e0a-87d94a891b47","name":"Property Specification","description":"Built-in type for specifying properties of object-type. This is the element-type of collection \"properties\" in the Vostan.Type.Type ","properties":[{"name":"Identifier","value_type":"57edf1cb-ac1e-49fa-bbb8-09658ed2ac19","mandatory":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf","description":"The identifier is used to define the programmatic (not necessarily human readable and certainly not localized)  name of the property. It is used as the field name in the JSON records, for example and for other purposes in the API calls. ","id":"id","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf"},{"name":"Name","value_type":"57edf1cb-ac1e-49fa-bbb8-09658ed2ac19","mandatory":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf","description":"The human-readable, localized name of the property. Used to dsiplay the property in the GUI for the user, as the title of the field in editor windows, property dialogs, new object creation dialogs, etc. ","id":"name","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf"},{"name":"Value Type","value_type":"360e8515-6962-4365-8e0a-87d94a891b47","mandatory":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf","description":"The restriction on the property to have only values of the given type. ","id":"value_type","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf"},{"name":"Is Mandatory","value_type":"beb2c92b-3e3e-41b8-9692-cd69b1f2c6f8","mandatory":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","description":"Specifies whether this property must be set upon object creation and always have  a valid value. Non mandatory property values may be missing in the object record in the database.","id":"mandatory","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","default_value":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf"},{"id":"default_value","name":"Default Value","value_type":"4279780d-d0cf-462d-b2bd-135a418b6e87","mandatory":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","description":"If default value is specified for a property, then upon creation of new object the property value will be set to this default. At the moment we look at default value only for mandatory properties. For non-mandatory properties this is ignored for now. In the future we may consider using this as the value of unspecified non mandatory properties.","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf","default_value":""},{"id":"readonly","name":"Is read-only","value_type":"beb2c92b-3e3e-41b8-9692-cd69b1f2c6f8","mandatory":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","description":"Read-only properties are displayed in the property editor without possibility to modify or unset them.","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","default_value":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf"},{"name":"Description","value_type":"6d084f31-309f-4cd4-8bcf-a703047af2cc","mandatory":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf","description":"In addition to name (used as title) the property specifications also provide a longer text, describing the meaning of the property. This is used in help windows, hint tooltips, etc in the GUI and for trainng the new users of the system.","id":"description","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf"},{"id":"visible","name":"Visible in GUI","value_type":"beb2c92b-3e3e-41b8-9692-cd69b1f2c6f8","mandatory":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","default_value":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","description":"This property indicates that this property should be stored in Metax records but should not be shown in the GUI standard dialogs (tree-view, property-editor, etc).","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf"},{"id":"icon","name":"Icon","value_type":"deef4328-2301-45da-8864-98b9bac4e369","mandatory":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","default_value":"","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","description":"Properties can have icons, icons will be displayed next to their name in the property-editor windows and other appearances of the object and/or property. ","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf","icon":""},{"id":"video","name":"Video","value_type":"f5b63f7f-4533-4b77-9e61-8bace086500c","mandatory":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","default_value":"","readonly":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","description":"","visible":"b06d4094-116b-4d2e-93ea-4398286e9acf","icon":""}],"collections":[],"id":"PropertySpecification","values":[],"literal":"508fddb1-933b-433c-a12c-2c76ad631519","methods":[]}